data.description: Beautiful Home that backs up to Birch Creek.  This Charming home features formal Dining Room, Living Room, Family Room on main floor and 4 Bedrooms and 2 baths upstairs. Main floor has the laundry room with a half bath . Two car garage attached to home and two detached  carports. Home has a custom stairlift that works great.    Large eat in kitchen with stainless steel appliances.  Home sits on 5.36 acres and  is surrounded with mature trees and beautiful landscaping.  Access to common ground where you can enjoy a  private picnic area and the Back Creek for some great fishing.  Paved roads all the way to the home.  Set your appointment now you won't want to miss this beautiful home.   GPS friendly.  The home also has the following features: 9' ceilings, septic pump, furnace, a/c are all under warranty and has been replaced in the last five years or less and crown molding thru out. Property is within 20-25 minutes of medical facilities and shopping.
